      "date": "2011-09-21 21:17:52.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(4 inline comments)\n\nSome style issues to be cleaned up so that the code is easier to maintain in the future.\n\nI assume you are already aware of the other patches for 2.6.38+ kernels in the LU-432 series (against b1_8) and/or in the pNFS patch in LU-438 (http://review.whamcloud.com/1343)?  Please coordinate any kernel update efforts with Lai Siyao and Yang Sheng so that you don't duplicate efforts.",
